org.openimaj.image.feature.local.keypoints

Class FloatKeypoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openimaj.image.feature.local.keypoints.FloatKeypoint
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, FeatureVectorProvider<FloatFV>, LocalFeature<KeypointLocation,FloatFV>, LocalFeatureVectorProvider<KeypointLocation,FloatFV>, LocationProvider<KeypointLocation>, Readable, ReadableASCII, ReadableBinary, ReadWriteable, VariableLength, Writeable, WriteableASCII, WriteableBinary, Coordinate, Point2d, ScaleSpacePoint

    public class FloatKeypoint
extends Object
implements Serializable, ScaleSpacePoint, LocalFeature<KeypointLocation,FloatFV>, VariableLength, Cloneable
    A local interest point with a location, scale, orientation and associated feature. The feature is stored as an array of floats.
    Author:
    Jonathon Hare (jsh2@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
